			the world. By concerning those natural beauties, we five young youths have decided 
			to inaugurate Z Star Homes in Nepal which is Nepal's first company having vision of
			home stay in Mustang and Mugu district of Nepal. Our company is  operated and promoted
			by ourselves and has enrolled professional guides who are responsible for providing a 
			wide range of culture, heritage and pilgrimage tours as well as other extra activities 
			that are connected with Himalayas destinations. Beside this, for being legalized, we have
			planned to get registration with Ministry of Tourism, Tourism Board, Office of Cottage and 
			Small Industry. Similarly, we have also planned to co-operate with Tax Office of Nepal and all
			tourism activities to display our company as civilized organization. Last but not least, we promise
			to create homely environment and fully entertain our guests by providing typical Nepali food items
			with suitable accommodation.
